# Frontend Architecture

Next.js 15 App Router + React 19. RSC default, `'use client'` explicit opt-in. State 4 kategori'de ayrılmış — her kategori tek sorumlu tool.

## Lean Design System (görsel — zorunlu)

Görünüm, tema, spacing ve hazır UI sınıfları için **`docs/lean-design-system/`** tek doğruluk kaynağıdır: `README.md` → `tokens.css` → `components.css`. Yeni ekran veya stil: magic değer yerine token / `ls-*` kullan; eksik token önce pakete eklenir (README “Token dışına çıkma”).

`apps/web/**/*.{tsx,ts,css}` üzerinde çalışırken **`26-lean-design-system.mdc`** otomatik eklenir — atla yok sayma.

## App Router Yapısı

```
apps/web/src/
├── app/
│   ├── (auth)/              # AuthLayout route group
│   │   ├── login/page.tsx
│   │   └── reset-password/page.tsx
│   ├── (app)/               # AppLayout route group
│   │   ├── layout.tsx       # Nested layout
│   │   ├── dashboard/page.tsx
│   │   ├── processes/...
│   │   ├── tasks/...
│   │   └── users/...
│   ├── (admin)/             # AdminLayout route group
│   │   └── admin/...
│   ├── layout.tsx           # Root layout
│   ├── middleware.ts        # Auth redirect
│   └── globals.css
├── components/
│   ├── ui/                  # shadcn/ui primitives
│   ├── shared/              # Cross-feature (Breadcrumb, DataTable, etc.)
│   ├── users/               # Feature: users
│   ├── processes/           # Feature: processes
│   └── ...
├── lib/
│   ├── api-client.ts        # Axios instance
│   ├── queries/             # TanStack Query hooks (per module)
│   ├── query-keys.ts        # Query key factory
│   └── utils.ts             # cn() helper vs.
├── hooks/                   # Custom hooks
├── stores/                  # Zustand stores
└── types/                   # Frontend-only types
```

## RSC vs Client Component

**Default: Server Component.** Client only when gerekli.

### Server Component (default)

- Markup-heavy static content
- Veriyi backend'den fetch (route-level `async` + `await`)
- SEO-sensitive içerik
- Sub-navigation component'lar

```typescript
// apps/web/src/app/(app)/dashboard/page.tsx
import { getServerSession } from '@/lib/session';

export default async function DashboardPage() {
  const session = await getServerSession();
  // Server-side data fetch — RSC
  return <DashboardWidgets userId={session.userId} />;
}
```

### Client Component

`'use client'` directive ekle. Tetikleyiciler:

- `useState`, `useEffect`, hook kullanımı
- Event handler (`onClick`, `onChange`)
- Browser API (`localStorage` kullanıyorsa — ki biz kullanmıyoruz)
- Third-party library olmalı client (örn. recharts, framer-motion)

```typescript
// apps/web/src/components/users/UserForm.tsx
'use client';

import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form';
// ...
```

### Geçiş Noktası

Route-level page default RSC. Interaction içeren feature component `'use client'`:

```typescript
// app/(app)/users/page.tsx — RSC (server)
import { UserList } from '@/components/users/UserList';

export default function UsersPage() {
  return (
    <div>
      <h1>Kullanıcılar</h1>
      <UserList />  {/* Client component within */}
    </div>
  );
}

// components/users/UserList.tsx — Client
'use client';
export function UserList() {
  const { data } = useUsersQuery();  // TanStack Query — client side
  // ...
}
```

## State Boundaries — 4 Kategori

Her state tek aracında:

### 1. Server State → TanStack Query

API'den gelen tüm data. Cache, invalidation, optimistic update.

```typescript
// lib/queries/users.ts
import { useQuery, useMutation, useQueryClient } from '@tanstack/react-query';
import { apiClient } from '@/lib/api-client';
import { queryKeys } from '@/lib/query-keys';

export function useUserQuery(id: string) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: queryKeys.users.detail(id),
    queryFn: () => apiClient.get(`/api/v1/users/${id}`).then((r) => r.data.data),
    staleTime: 60_000,  // 1 dk
  });
}

export function useCreateUserMutation() {
  const queryClient = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: (input) => apiClient.post('/api/v1/users', input).then((r) => r.data.data),
    onSuccess: () => queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.users.lists() }),
  });
}
```

**Server state'i Zustand'a koyma.** "Sync" çalışmaz — stale data.

### 2. Client Session State → Zustand

User session, UI preferences, cross-component memory (server-independent).

```typescript
// stores/auth-store.ts
import { create } from 'zustand';

interface AuthStore {
  accessToken: string | null;
  csrfToken: string | null;
  currentUser: AuthenticatedUser | null;
  setAuth: (token: string, csrf: string, user: AuthenticatedUser) => void;
  clearAuth: () => void;
}

export const useAuthStore = create<AuthStore>((set) => ({
  accessToken: null,
  csrfToken: null,
  currentUser: null,
  setAuth: (accessToken, csrfToken, currentUser) => 
    set({ accessToken, csrfToken, currentUser }),
  clearAuth: () => set({ accessToken: null, csrfToken: null, currentUser: null }),
}));
```

**Persist YASAK.** Auth tokens memory only (refresh ile yeniden alınır).

### 3. URL State → Search Params

Filter, sort, pagination, tab state. Shareable + bookmarkable + back button works.

```typescript
'use client';
import { useSearchParams, useRouter } from 'next/navigation';

export function UserListFilters() {
  const searchParams = useSearchParams();
  const router = useRouter();

  const status = searchParams.get('status') ?? 'active';
  
  const setStatus = (newStatus: string) => {
    const params = new URLSearchParams(searchParams);
    params.set('status', newStatus);
    router.push(`?${params.toString()}`);
  };

  return <Select value={status} onValueChange={setStatus}>...</Select>;
}
```

TanStack Query key'i URL param'a bağlanır:

```typescript
const status = searchParams.get('status') ?? 'active';
const { data } = useQuery({
  queryKey: queryKeys.users.list({ status }),
  queryFn: () => apiClient.get(`/users?status=${status}`).then(...),
});
```

URL değişince query otomatik refetch — cache key değişti.

### 4. Form State → react-hook-form

Form input değerleri, validation, submit state. Forms rule'u (22-frontend-forms) detay.

